snippet.textDisplay: Hey Vincent. Hope you don't have any serious effects from the virus. Good to see you are still teaching. I'm 75 now and so far I'm staying well. Living in a rural area and staying safe.  Thanks for this video. I worked with you for a few years. Marie Waddell.
